    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b You\u2019ve gotta see this beauty \u2013 it\u2019s honestly like it just rolled right off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and it\u2019s in absolutely pristine, flawless condition inside and out. It drives like a dream and looks even better in person. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been loved and kept in tip-top shape, this is the one for you! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I\u2019d love to see it go to a great new home! \ud83d\ude97\u2728",
