    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade E46 M3, showcasing the pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering. Power is derived from the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring six individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure Double-VANOS system for razor-sharp throttle response. This example features the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual transmission, delivering torque to a variable M differential lock. The chassis remains structurally flawless with documented subframe reinforcement and a suspension geometry that adheres to strict factory specifications. Every mechanical component, from the rod bearings to the cooling system, has been meticulously maintained to original tolerances. This is a concourse-level specimen with zero deferred maintenance, offering the purest analog driving experience.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
