    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional find: a vehicle that looks and drives as though it just rolled off the showroom floor. This car has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage, preserving its stunning, mirror-like exterior finish without a single swirl mark or stone chip. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine, factory-fresh condition; the premium leather upholstery shows zero signs of wear, and every electronic feature operates with precision. Mechanically, the vehicle is beyond reproach, boasting a complete, documented service history and a whisper-quiet engine that delivers a smooth, powerful performance. From the flawless alloy wheels to the untouched undercarriage, no detail has been overlooked. This is a rare opportunity to own a collector-grade example of engineering excellence, perfect for the buyer who demands nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
