    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presented here is an automotive specimen of the highest caliber. This vehicle remains in impeccable, showroom-ready condition, reflecting a standard of maintenance that borders on the obsessive. Every detail, from the flawless exterior finish to the untouched interior upholstery, confirms its status as a premier investment for the discerning collector. We invite you to experience a level of refinement rarely encountered in the pre-owned market.",
