    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly a little sad to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014it honestly feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been pampered since day one, kept in a garage, and driven very gently. If you\u2019re looking for something that\u2019s basically flawless and ready for a road trip today, this is the one for you. It still has that fresh feel and drives like a dream. Come take a look, you won\u2019t be disappointed!",
