      "description": "Offering a superlative E46 M3 in collector-grade condition. This specimen features the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six, exhibiting perfect compression across all cylinders and a meticulously serviced VANOS system. The high-revving powerplant is mated to a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox, delivering power through a variable M differential lock. The chassis remains factory-stiff with a documented rear subframe reinforcement, ensuring the hydraulic steering rack provides unfiltered feedback. From the pristine underside to the tight tolerances of the individual throttle bodies, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering. All bushings and suspension components are in peak operational state, offering a driving dynamic that mirrors its original delivery specifications.",
